Jacob Cawsey (born 7 May 1993) is an English footballer who last played for the St. Louis Ambush of the Major Arena Soccer League.
After realising his lack of talent he now resides in SW London playing for Step 8 side Goldfingers FC. He got a red card on his debut & scored his first goal in a 4-1 victory against AFC Ewell.
